jquery.shorturl.js
==================

A jQuery plugin that allows you to shorten URLs using different services.


**[GitHub project](https://github.com/carlol/jquery.shorturl.js)**


----------

At present, the plugin allows access only to goo.gl API. Additional features will ensure support for more services.

**@see** a simple example: [**link**][1]


  [1]: https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/21498650/jquery_shorturl/example/index.html
